    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300033706_6_25083-25163",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "25083-25163",
      "markText": "吉哈德的明确宗旨是通过对战争之境发动不懈的圣战使全人类皈依伊斯兰教或服从穆斯林的统治。不能与异教敌人缔结永久的和约，而且任何临时停战协定的时间都不能超过10年。",
      "totalCount": 210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300033706&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=25083&rangeEnd=25163",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0a32c60813ab73aag0169ed?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=25083&rangeEnd=25163"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300033706_7_13218-13277",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "13218-13277",
      "markText": "他想必的确是一位善于鼓舞人心的演讲家，在克莱蒙的6个月中，他成功招募了一支军队（大部分是贫民），人数超过了1.5万人。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300033706&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=13218&rangeEnd=13277",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0a32c60813ab73aag0169ed?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=13218&rangeEnd=13277"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300033706_6_8535-8594",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "8535-8594",
      "markText": "312年，君士坦丁大帝在经历了一次“异象”后决心皈依基督教（那时是一个较小的东方教派），基督教因此突然登上了世界舞台。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300033706&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8535&rangeEnd=8594",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0a32c60813ab73aag0169ed?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8535&rangeEnd=8594"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300033706_8_5138-5159",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "5138-5159",
      "markText": "作为假定的罪恶之源，女人同时被逐出了营地。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300033706&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5138&rangeEnd=5159",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f0a32c60813ab73aag0169ed?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5138&rangeEnd=5159"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300033706_6_18153-18233",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "18153-18233",
      "markText": "穆斯林不要求“有经人”（Peoples of the Book，例如犹太人和基督徒）彻底臣服并立即皈依伊斯兰教，而是允许他们在缴纳人头税的前提下保留自己的信仰。",
